{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":365,"text":"[His Holiness Pope Francis\nFilmed in Vatican City"},{"time":2805,"text":"First shown at TED2017]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":4900,"text":"Good evening – or, good morning,\nI am not sure what time it is there."},{"time":12700,"text":"Regardless of the hour, I am thrilled\nto be participating in your conference."},{"time":20696,"text":"I very much like its title\n– \"The Future You\" –"},{"time":25820,"text":"because, while looking at tomorrow,\nit invites us to open a dialogue today,"},{"time":33500,"text":"to look at the future through a \"you.\""},{"time":39284,"text":"\"The Future You:\""},{"time":41820,"text":"the future is made of yous,\nit is made of encounters,"},{"time":49660,"text":"because life flows\nthrough our relations with others."},{"time":54460,"text":"Quite a few years of life"},{"time":56380,"text":"have strengthened my conviction"},{"time":59900,"text":"that each and everyone's existence\nis deeply tied to that of others:"},{"time":67719,"text":"life is not time merely passing by,\nlife is about interactions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":76380,"text":"As I meet, or lend an ear\nto those who are sick,"},{"time":81620,"text":"to the migrants\nwho face terrible hardships"},{"time":86380,"text":"in search of a brighter future,"},{"time":89220,"text":"to prison inmates who carry\na hell of pain inside their hearts,"},{"time":93820,"text":"and to those, many of them young,\nwho cannot find a job,"},{"time":98940,"text":"I often find myself wondering:"},{"time":103460,"text":"\"Why them and not me?\""},{"time":109055,"text":"I, myself, was born\nin a family of migrants;"},{"time":114540,"text":"my father, my grandparents,\nlike many other Italians,"},{"time":119980,"text":"left for Argentina"},{"time":122060,"text":"and met the fate of those\nwho are left with nothing."},{"time":128220,"text":"I could have very well ended up\namong today's \"discarded\" people."},{"time":133900,"text":"And that's why I always ask myself,\ndeep in my heart:"},{"time":138641,"text":"\"Why them and not me?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":144220,"text":"First and foremost, I would love it\nif this meeting could help to remind us"},{"time":148740,"text":"that we all need each other,"},{"time":153418,"text":"none of us is an island,"},{"time":157100,"text":"an autonomous and independent \"I,\"\nseparated from the other,"},{"time":162020,"text":"and we can only build the future\nby standing together, including everyone."},{"time":170140,"text":"We don’t think about it often,\nbut everything is connected,"},{"time":176180,"text":"and we need to restore\nour connections to a healthy state."},{"time":181725,"text":"Even the harsh judgment I hold in my heart"},{"time":184726,"text":"against my brother or my sister,"},{"time":187820,"text":"the open wound that was never cured,\nthe offense that was never forgiven,"},{"time":191900,"text":"the rancor that is only going to hurt me,"},{"time":194940,"text":"are all instances of a fight\nthat I carry within me,"},{"time":198266,"text":"a flare deep in my heart\nthat needs to be extinguished"},{"time":200980,"text":"before it goes up in flames,\nleaving only ashes behind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207220,"text":"Many of us, nowadays,"},{"time":210180,"text":"seem to believe that a happy future\nis something impossible to achieve."},{"time":215740,"text":"While such concerns\nmust be taken very seriously,"},{"time":219300,"text":"they are not invincible."},{"time":222620,"text":"They can be overcome when we don't lock\nour door to the outside world."},{"time":229780,"text":"Happiness can only be discovered"},{"time":233300,"text":"as a gift of harmony between the whole\nand each single component."},{"time":239100,"text":"Even science – and you know it\nbetter than I do –"},{"time":242700,"text":"points to an understanding of reality"},{"time":247780,"text":"as a place where every element connects\nand interacts with everything else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256820,"text":"And this brings me to my second message."},{"time":262780,"text":"How wonderful would it be"},{"time":265859,"text":"if the growth of scientific\nand technological innovation"},{"time":271580,"text":"would come along with more equality\nand social inclusion."},{"time":278780,"text":"How wonderful would it be,\nwhile we discover faraway planets,"},{"time":284940,"text":"to rediscover the needs of the brothers\nand sisters orbiting around us."},{"time":292260,"text":"How wonderful would it be if solidarity,"},{"time":295500,"text":"this beautiful and, at times,\ninconvenient word,"},{"time":299940,"text":"were not simply reduced to social work,"},{"time":303940,"text":"and became, instead, the default attitude"},{"time":307620,"text":"in political, economic\nand scientific choices,"},{"time":313220,"text":"as well as in the relationships\namong individuals, peoples and countries."},{"time":319260,"text":"Only by educating people\nto a true solidarity"},{"time":323292,"text":"will we be able to overcome"},{"time":326992,"text":"the \"culture of waste,\""},{"time":331610,"text":"which doesn't concern only food and goods"},{"time":337420,"text":"but, first and foremost, the people"},{"time":340100,"text":"who are cast aside\nby our techno-economic systems"},{"time":345940,"text":"which, without even realizing it,"},{"time":350340,"text":"are now putting products\nat their core, instead of people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357340,"text":"Solidarity is a term that many wish\nto erase from the dictionary."},{"time":365380,"text":"Solidarity, however,\nis not an automatic mechanism."},{"time":370380,"text":"It cannot be programmed or controlled."},{"time":373660,"text":"It is a free response born\nfrom the heart of each and everyone."},{"time":378700,"text":"Yes, a free response!"},{"time":382220,"text":"When one realizes"},{"time":383460,"text":"that life, even in the middle\nof so many contradictions, is a gift,"},{"time":388220,"text":"that love is the source\nand the meaning of life,"},{"time":392700,"text":"how can they withhold their urge\nto do good to another fellow being?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":399060,"text":"In order to do good,"},{"time":400860,"text":"we need memory, we need courage\nand we need creativity."},{"time":408300,"text":"And I know that TED\ngathers many creative minds."},{"time":417180,"text":"Yes, love does require\na creative, concrete"},{"time":424192,"text":"and ingenious attitude."},{"time":427750,"text":"Good intentions and conventional formulas,"},{"time":432865,"text":"so often used to appease\nour conscience, are not enough."},{"time":439036,"text":"Let us help each other,\nall together, to remember"},{"time":442900,"text":"that the other is not\na statistic or a number."},{"time":447997,"text":"The other has a face."},{"time":450346,"text":"The \"you\" is always a real presence,"},{"time":454593,"text":"a person to take care of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":461454,"text":"There is a parable Jesus told\nto help us understand the difference"},{"time":466860,"text":"between those who'd rather not be bothered\nand those who take care of the other."},{"time":475380,"text":"I am sure you have heard it before.\nIt is the Parable of the Good Samaritan."},{"time":482100,"text":"When Jesus was asked:\n\"Who is my neighbor?\" -"},{"time":486180,"text":"namely, \"Who should I take care of?\" -"},{"time":491020,"text":"he told this story, the story of a man"},{"time":495061,"text":"who had been assaulted, robbed,\nbeaten and abandoned along a dirt road."},{"time":502340,"text":"Upon seeing him, a priest and a Levite,\ntwo very influential people of the time,"},{"time":509180,"text":"walked past him without stopping to help."},{"time":513580,"text":"After a while, a Samaritan, a very much\ndespised ethnicity at the time, walked by."},{"time":520773,"text":"Seeing the injured man\nlying on the ground,"},{"time":526180,"text":"he did not ignore him\nas if he weren't even there."},{"time":531572,"text":"Instead, he felt compassion for this man,"},{"time":535775,"text":"which compelled him to act\nin a very concrete manner."},{"time":544220,"text":"He poured oil and wine\non the wounds of the helpless man,"},{"time":549052,"text":"brought him to a hostel"},{"time":550980,"text":"and paid out of his pocket\nfor him to be assisted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555900,"text":"The story of the Good Samaritan\nis the story of today’s humanity."},{"time":560740,"text":"People's paths are riddled with suffering,"},{"time":565700,"text":"as everything is centered around money,\nand things, instead of people."},{"time":572940,"text":"And often there is this habit, by people\nwho call themselves \"respectable,\""},{"time":578660,"text":"of not taking care of the others,"},{"time":581882,"text":"thus leaving behind thousands\nof human beings, or entire populations,"},{"time":589072,"text":"on the side of the road."},{"time":593620,"text":"Fortunately, there are also those\nwho are creating a new world"},{"time":598272,"text":"by taking care of the other,\neven out of their own pockets."},{"time":604460,"text":"Mother Teresa actually said:"},{"time":608445,"text":"\"One cannot love,\nunless it is at their own expense.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":615140,"text":"We have so much to do,\nand we must do it together."},{"time":621100,"text":"But how can we do that\nwith all the evil we breathe every day?"},{"time":626957,"text":"Thank God,"},{"time":628432,"text":"no system can nullify our desire\nto open up to the good,"},{"time":632790,"text":"to compassion and to our capacity\nto react against evil,"},{"time":636833,"text":"all of which stem\nfrom deep within our hearts."},{"time":639293,"text":"Now you might tell me,"},{"time":640741,"text":"\"Sure, these are beautiful words,"},{"time":642460,"text":"but I am not the Good Samaritan,\nnor Mother Teresa of Calcutta.\""},{"time":647833,"text":"On the contrary: we are precious,\neach and every one of us."},{"time":652661,"text":"Each and every one of us\nis irreplaceable in the eyes of God."},{"time":658980,"text":"Through the darkness of today's conflicts,"},{"time":663260,"text":"each and every one of us\ncan become a bright candle,"},{"time":667820,"text":"a reminder that light\nwill overcome darkness,"},{"time":672900,"text":"and never the other way around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676557,"text":"To Christians,\nthe future does have a name,"},{"time":681877,"text":"and its name is Hope."},{"time":685220,"text":"Feeling hopeful does not mean\nto be optimistically naïve"},{"time":691100,"text":"and ignore the tragedy humanity is facing."},{"time":697940,"text":"Hope is the virtue of a heart"},{"time":700940,"text":"that doesn't lock itself into darkness,\nthat doesn't dwell on the past,"},{"time":706020,"text":"does not simply get by in the present,\nbut is able to see a tomorrow."},{"time":712500,"text":"Hope is the door\nthat opens onto the future."},{"time":715180,"text":"Hope is a humble, hidden seed of life"},{"time":720460,"text":"that, with time,\nwill develop into a large tree."},{"time":725780,"text":"It is like some invisible yeast\nthat allows the whole dough to grow,"},{"time":731980,"text":"that brings flavor to all aspects of life."},{"time":735220,"text":"And it can do so much,"},{"time":737940,"text":"because a tiny flicker of light\nthat feeds on hope"},{"time":745531,"text":"is enough to shatter\nthe shield of darkness."},{"time":750717,"text":"A single individual\nis enough for hope to exist,"},{"time":755420,"text":"and that individual can be you."},{"time":759980,"text":"And then there will be another \"you,\"\nand another \"you,\""},{"time":766282,"text":"and it turns into an \"us.\""},{"time":769238,"text":"And so, does hope begin\nwhen we have an \"us?\""},{"time":773519,"text":"No."},{"time":774687,"text":"Hope began with one \"you.\""},{"time":777580,"text":"When there is an \"us,\"\nthere begins a revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":785240,"text":"The third message\nI would like to share today"},{"time":788700,"text":"is, indeed, about revolution:\nthe revolution of tenderness."},{"time":795220,"text":"And what is tenderness?"},{"time":797980,"text":"It is the love that comes close\nand becomes real."},{"time":801180,"text":"It is a movement\nthat starts from our heart"},{"time":803380,"text":"and reaches the eyes,\nthe ears and the hands."},{"time":807580,"text":"Tenderness means to use\nour eyes to see the other,"},{"time":812540,"text":"our ears to hear the other,"},{"time":815345,"text":"to listen to the children, the poor,\nthose who are afraid of the future."},{"time":821653,"text":"To listen also to the silent cry\nof our common home,"},{"time":827420,"text":"of our sick and polluted earth."},{"time":830740,"text":"Tenderness means to use\nour hands and our heart"},{"time":836460,"text":"to comfort the other,"},{"time":839260,"text":"to take care of those in need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":842900,"text":"Tenderness is the language\nof the young children,"},{"time":848111,"text":"of those who need the other."},{"time":851616,"text":"A child’s love for mom and dad"},{"time":856980,"text":"grows through their touch, their gaze,\ntheir voice, their tenderness."},{"time":864740,"text":"I like when I hear parents"},{"time":867060,"text":"talk to their babies,\nadapting to the little child,"},{"time":873340,"text":"sharing the same level of communication."},{"time":881340,"text":"This is tenderness:\nbeing on the same level as the other."},{"time":888100,"text":"God himself descended into Jesus\nto be on our level."},{"time":895540,"text":"This is the same path\nthe Good Samaritan took."},{"time":899260,"text":"This is the path that Jesus himself took."},{"time":903100,"text":"He lowered himself,"},{"time":904820,"text":"he lived his entire human existence"},{"time":907380,"text":"practicing the real,\nconcrete language of love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":912300,"text":"Yes, tenderness is the path of choice"},{"time":915780,"text":"for the strongest,\nmost courageous men and women."},{"time":922980,"text":"Tenderness is not weakness;\nit is fortitude."},{"time":927100,"text":"It is the path of solidarity,\nthe path of humility."},{"time":932900,"text":"Please, allow me to say it loud and clear:"},{"time":936020,"text":"the more powerful you are,"},{"time":938700,"text":"the more your actions\nwill have an impact on people,"},{"time":943460,"text":"the more responsible you are\nto act humbly."},{"time":948380,"text":"If you don’t, your power will ruin you,\nand you will ruin the other."},{"time":957860,"text":"There is a saying in Argentina:"},{"time":960107,"text":"\"Power is like drinking gin\non an empty stomach.\""},{"time":967740,"text":"You feel dizzy, you get drunk,\nyou lose your balance,"},{"time":974900,"text":"and you will end up hurting yourself\nand those around you,"},{"time":980380,"text":"if you don’t connect your power\nwith humility and tenderness."},{"time":987580,"text":"Through humility and concrete love,\non the other hand,"},{"time":992292,"text":"power – the highest, the strongest one –\nbecomes a service, a force for good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001740,"text":"The future of humankind isn't exclusively\nin the hands of politicians,"},{"time":1007340,"text":"of great leaders, of big companies."},{"time":1011460,"text":"Yes, they do hold\nan enormous responsibility."},{"time":1014260,"text":"But the future is, most of all,\nin the hands of those people"},{"time":1019100,"text":"who recognize the other as a \"you\""},{"time":1023086,"text":"and themselves as part of an \"us.\""},{"time":1028019,"text":"We all need each other."},{"time":1031019,"text":"And so, please, think of me\nas well with tenderness,"},{"time":1036153,"text":"so that I can fulfill the task\nI have been given"},{"time":1039551,"text":"for the good of the other,"},{"time":1041998,"text":"of each and every one, of all of you,"},{"time":1045739,"text":"of all of us."},{"time":1048080,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}